title: I Don't Consider Myself A Doubler with Eddie Daniels
description:
Back for another round of videos with Team Backun, Eddie Daniels sits down with us to discuss the role of Doublers and Triplers in Jazz and Classical music, and what it takes to master multiple instruments. Eddie takes you on a whirlwind tour of his experience with these instruments and gives some insight into playing an instrument outside your comfort zone.

In this video, Eddie is playing a Prototype Backun Bb Cocobolo Clarinet with Gold Keys, along with a Fatboy Cocobolo Barrel and Traditional Grenadilla Bell. The Mouthpiece? A prototype of the new Backun Eddie Daniels Classical mouthpiece available late 2011!
